HEADWORD: Brugmansia
<hw>Brugmansia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a genus of plants of the
nightshade family, including some plants often placed in the genus
<gen>Datura</gen>, such as the angel's trumpets.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Brugmansia</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
